    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_2958_51_8",
    "text": "When I'm feeling good and energized I'm usually pretty quick on my feet and friendly, but being even a little tired makes me dull and anxious.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_2958_98_2",
    "text": "When I sit down and think and try to relax I have an easier time identifying how I'm feeling and becoming grounded in the moment, but it takes conscious effort.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_3042_4_37",
    "text": "I was on this pill called lamotrigine and it was working, and helping with the anxiety and irritability.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_3075_19_3",
    "text": "I'm easily agitated and i don't want anyone around me, I haven't been able to sleep I literally took nyquil yesterday just to help sleep nothing works.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_335_3_449",
    "text": "I tried to calm down, but I couldn't.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_386_117_0",
    "text": "If I try to distract myself with the phone for example it often helps but if the panick attack manages to overwhelm me while I try to distract myself on the phone it comes back even worse.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_600_1120_5",
    "text": "I'm restless and overwhelmed by thoughts.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_708_315_0",
    "text": "My dog is trained to comfort me when I have anxiety, be a physical barrier between me and people when I get panicky, and provide an excuse to leave a situation i.e. he needs to go potty/eat/drink.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_716_38_24",
    "text": "I am anxious much of the time.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_717_85_15",
    "text": "I feel unreasonable and childish that I can't just nut up about it but I keep going back and forth between acceptance, anger, sadness and anxiety about my living situation.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_71_289_0",
    "text": "I have a very hard time just sitting still sometimes.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_752_56_15",
    "text": "I've just been up all night cold sweating and shaking because I'm anxious.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_888_1550_2",
    "text": "Right now I am feeling very overwhelmed and nervous.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_888_1808_5",
    "text": "Still anxious of course it is tearing me up.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_8_341_6",
    "text": "I have more energy, confidence, less fatigue, less anxiety, slightly less depression, and a bit better sex drive so far, and it's still very early in my treatment, so it should improve even more.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_90_133_4",
    "text": "In addition when I notice the anxiety ramping up from, say, a stressful day at work... a few minutes of Box Breathing helps me to refocus and counter a panic attack before it starts. (",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_993_130_2",
    "text": "But right now I just feel restless and weird.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_993_456_2",
    "text": "I had restless legs for weeks.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  },
  {
    "symptom_id": 13,
    "docid": "s_993_842_1",
    "text": "I feel bursts of positivity...then restlessness and end up doing nothing.",
    "bdi_query": 11,
    "bdi_name": "Agitation",
    "majority": 1,
    "consensus": 1,
    "type": "agreement",
    "source": "erisk2023"
  }
]